-- ALTER VIEW kpiemail.dim_target_sro
-- AS
SELECT
[CICLO]
,[DIVISAO]
,[TARGET_SRO_CRM]
,[TARGET_SRO_VISITA]
,[TARGET_SRO_MEDIA_DIA]
,[TARGET_SRO_COACHING]
,[TARGET_SRO_COB]
,[KEY_DIVISAO_CICLO]
FROM
    OPENROWSET(
        BULK 'https://gsksynapseaccount.dfs.core.windows.net/gskoutputfiles/Email & KPI Visitacao/dimensao_target_sro.parquet',
        FORMAT='PARQUET'
    ) WITH(
[CICLO]					VARCHAR(50) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[DIVISAO]				  VARCHAR(50) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[TARGET_SRO_CRM]		  VARCHAR(50) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[TARGET_SRO_VISITA]	  VARCHAR(50) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[TARGET_SRO_MEDIA_DIA]	  VARCHAR(50) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[TARGET_SRO_COACHING]	  VARCHAR(50) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[TARGET_SRO_COB]		  VARCHAR(50) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[KEY_DIVISAO_CICLO]	  VARCHAR(50) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
    ) AS ROW
